dWord","Ether"],"8:25"],";"]]],["div",{"id":"f5","uri":"/scriptures/tg/murder.f5","order":".000.6915"},["ul.index",["li","he that",["i","kills"],"shall not have forgiveness:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.18"},"D&C 42:18"],";"],["li","if any … shall",["i","kill"],"they shall be delivered up:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/42.79"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"42:79"],";"],["li","commit no",["i","murder"],"whereby to shed innocent blood:",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.19"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"132:19"],"; (",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/132.27"},["span.padWord","D&C"],"132:27"],"; )"]]],["div",{"id":"f6","uri":"/scriptures/tg/murder.f6","order":".000.6916"},["ul.index",["li","Cain said: Truly I am Mahan … that I may",["i","murder"],":",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/pgp/moses/5.31"},"Moses 5:31"],";"]]]]],"refs":null}
